title: Failure to enforce any provision of the Terms of Service does not constitute a waiver of such provision
quoteText: The <abbr>OTW</abbr>'s failure to enforce any part of the <abbr>ToS</abbr> will not waive the <abbr>OTW</abbr>'s ability to enforce it
